<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="B" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Buy1" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Buy,</orth> in the phrase <emph>God buy you,</emph> a contraction from <emph>God be with you,</emph> in the sense of the modern good-bye (M. Edd. generally <emph>be with you</emph>): <bibl n="shak. ayl 3.2.273" default="NO" valid="yes">As III, 2, 273</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ayl 4.1.31" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 1, 31</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ayl 5.3.41" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 3, 41</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tn 4.2.108" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. IV, 2, 108</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h5 4.3.6" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 IV, 3, 6</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h5 5.1.70" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 1, 70</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 3.2.73" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A III, 2, 73</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tro 3.3.294" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. III, 3, 294</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 2.1.69" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. II, 1, 69</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 2.2.575" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 2, 575</bibl> (Qq <emph>God buy to you</emph>). <bibl n="shak. ham 4.4.30" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 4, 30</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 4.5.200" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 5, 200</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. oth 1.3.189" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. I, 3, 189</bibl> (here Ff., certainly with good reason, <emph>God be with you</emph>). <bibl n="shak. oth 3.3.375" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 3, 375</bibl>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>